org.anchoranalysis.plugin.quick.bean.experiment

Class QuickMultiDatasetExperiment<T extends InputFromManager,S>

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<Experiment>
      • Experiment
        • QuickMultiDatasetExperiment<T,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - input-object type
    S - shared-state
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AssociateXmlUponLoad, ReplaceInputManager, ReplaceOutputManager

    public class QuickMultiDatasetExperiment<T extends InputFromManager,S>
extends Experiment
implements ReplaceInputManager, ReplaceOutputManager
    Makes a lot of assumptions, that allows us to reduce the number of inputs to an InputOutputExperiment.

    Normally, runs an experiment on all data-sets in *datasets*.

    However, in debug-mode datasetSpecific is used (if non-empty), otherwise the first dataset is used.
